[[Disney Cinemagic (Germany)|Disney Cinemagic]]}} '''''''Disney XD''''''' is a [[Germany]] TV channel that replaced [[Jetix (Germany)|Jetix Germany]] on October 9, 2009. On April 15, 2010 it replaced [[Toon Disney (Germany)|Toon Disney Germany]], too. At the same time Disney XD +1 started its broadcast in Germany. ==History== Disney XD started as [[Jetix (Germany)|Fox Kids Germany]] on October 2000. It aired shows like [[Get Ed]], [[Jackie Chan Adventures]] and others. As its rebrand to Disney XD on October 9, 2009, it is still airing these type of shows. ===Disney XD=== When [[Jetix (Germany)|Jetix Germany]] successfully closed down on October 9, 2009 with Disney XD taking its place.
